  "description": "",
  "frame_eqs": "// PER_FRAME CODE FOR WARP SHADER PRESET\n\n// Audio reactivity - connect to MilkDrop's audio analysis\nbass_thresh = 0.6;\ntreb_thresh = 0.4;\nmid_thresh = 0.5;\n\n// Normalized audio values (0-1 range)\nbass_norm = bass/bass_att;\ntreb_norm = treb/treb_att;\nmid_norm = mid/mid_att;\n\n// Combined audio energy\naudio_energy = (bass_norm + treb_norm + mid_norm)/3;\n\n// Time-based animation\ntime_speed = 0.5 + bass_norm*0.5;\ntime = time + 0.033*time_speed; // frame-time aware animation\n\n// Mouse position simulation using q variables\n// q1 = horizontal position (simulated mouse X)\nq1 = 0.5 + sin(time*0.3)*0.5;\n// q2 = vertical position (simulated mouse Y)\nq2 = 0.5 + cos(time*0.4)*0.5;\n// q3 = click state (0 or 1)\nbeat = if (bass > 2, int(rand(2)), beat); //For simulated click (q3)\nq3 = beat; // Set to 1 for \"clicked\" effect\n\n// Distortion parameters based on audio\nq4 = .2 + bass_norm/2.5; // DISTORTION factor\nq5 = .0575 + treb_norm/2.5; // Number of arms\n\n// Color cycling\nq6 = time*0.1; // Color cycle speed\nq7 = 0.5 + sin(time*0.2)*0.5; // Color variation 1\nq8 = 0.5 + cos(time*0.25)*0.5; // Color variation 2\n\n// Warp parameters\nwarp_scale = 1.0 - mid_norm*0.3;\nzoom = 1.0 + bass_norm*0.5;\nrot = time*0.1 + treb_norm*0.2;",
